channel.title: Zenith slave frozen, cant finish dung rooms
channel.description:
Hi, i'm making a runescape private server using zenith server and client. I have stumbled across an error and not quite sure how to fix it. Basically you can't finish any of the dungoneering floors because "zenith's slave" is only examinable not attackable therefore the strange wall exit ladder won't open to finish the dungeon.
here is a picture [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/qKjho8P.png[/img]
